OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA bright start in the east,
OL,6,Fbut cloud and some patchy rain will
OL,7,Fgradually spread across the region.
OL,8,FRemaining cloudy into the afternoon
OL,9,Fwith some heavier rain arriving
OL,10,Fovernight. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FFurther rain and strong winds on
OL,14,FWednesday, with sunshine and showers
OL,15,Fon Thursday. Showers more isolated on
OL,16,FFriday. Feeling a little warmer than
OL,17,Fof late, especially in any sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
